biotools.summary:
A Robot Annotator for Argonaute Proteins.

Welcome to AgoNotes home page! AGONOTES is an online service tool to identify Argonaute protein in proteins of all domains of life and annotate the argonaute domains. Users can submit any protein with fasta formation into the input field, or save proteins as a file ended with .faa, .fasta, .fa or .txt and then upload this file
